ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Marystown-Burin Area Chamber of Commerce CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for THE MARYSTOWN-BURIN AREA CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Newfoundland and Labrador (a) to change its name to THE BURIN PENINSULA CHAMBER OF COMMERCE; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to the Burin Peninsula south of Swift Current.
